  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Junior Treasury Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>[Job ID: 1461269]</strong></p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Provide treasury and financial support to Bridgestone Group companies, including loan/credit arrangements and foreign exchange (FX) transactions.</li><li>Manage borrowing from financial institutions and group companies, and on-lending to group entities.</li><li>Execute and support FX transactions, including spot, forward, and Non-Deliverable Forward (NDF) dealings.</li><li>Prepare treasury-related documentation and liaise with financial institutions and group companies for transaction execution and settlement.</li><li>Monitor incoming and outgoing remittances to ensure timely and accurate settlement; investigate and resolve discrepancies.</li><li>Support regional liquidity management activities, including cash pooling, and operate treasury systems such as Internet Banking, FXall, and Reval.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements / Preferences</strong></p><ul><li>Degree in Finance, Banking, Treasury, or a related discipline.</li><li>Prior experience in treasury or treasury administration within a financial institution or finance-related company is preferred.</li><li>Strong numerical aptitude with attention to detail.</li><li>Team player with good communication and coordination skills.</li><li>Fluent in spoken and written English.</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Ong Kang Quan Ryan<br />EA Personnel Registration Number: R23116952<br />EA License No.: 07C5771</p>",
